    'en_US' => '<p><strong>ONLINE SUMBISSION</strong></p>
<ol>
<li class="show">The articles are submitted to the editorial staff via an electronic submission system that allows to speed up the registration of the article, its consideration, the authors can also monitor the article processing.</li>
